<% content_for :title, "About — AcquireTMT" %>

<section class="bg-brand-900 text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-28">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-300">About</p>
    <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-4xl font-serif text-5xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
      The M&A advisory firm
      <span class="text-brand-300">built for TMT founders.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-xl text-white/80">
      AcquireTMT pairs AI-assisted buyer discovery and valuation context with experienced M&A advisors, so technology-enabled business owners can run a structured, confidential sale process.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium leading-tight text-brand-900 sm:text-5xl">
          Why we exist
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
          <p>
            Selling a technology business is often opaque. Owners struggle to know what their company is worth, who the right buyers are, and how to run a process without tipping off competitors, customers, or staff.
          </p>
          <p>
            Traditional advisors rely on manual buyer research and slow, fragmented processes. We built software to automate the analyst work — buyer mapping, valuation context, market comps — so our advisors focus on judgment and dealmaking.
          </p>
          <p>
            The result is a faster, more transparent path to a confident exit for owners of SaaS, MSP, telecom, digital media, cybersecurity, and other tech-enabled businesses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <% [
          ["$1M–$100M", "Revenue range we focus on"],
          ["TMT", "Technology, media & telecom specialists"],
          ["AI-assisted", "Buyer discovery and valuation context"],
          ["Confidential", "Process designed to protect your business"]
        ].each do |stat, label| %>
          <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-brand-50 p-8">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium text-brand-900"><%= stat %></p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600"><%= label %></p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-brand-50 py-24 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-300">How we work</p>
      <h2 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl font-medium leading-tight text-brand-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Software does the analysis. Advisors do the deal.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <% [
        ["search", "Map the market", "AI identifies strategic acquirers, PE platforms, family offices, and search funds that fit your profile."],
        ["bar-chart-3", "Frame the value", "Valuation context and market comps position your revenue quality the way buyers underwrite it."],
        ["handshake", "Run the process", "Experienced advisors manage confidential outreach, offers, and diligence to close."]
      ].each do |icon, title, desc| %>
        <div class="rounded-sm border border-brand-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
          <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-brand-900 text-brand-300">
            <%= lucide_icon icon, class: "h-6 w-6" %>
          </span>
          <h3 class="mt-6 font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-brand-900"><%= title %></h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600"><%= desc %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-brand-900 py-24 text-white sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-medium leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">
      Thinking about an exit?
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/70">
      Start with a free valuation snapshot or speak with an advisor confidentially.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <%= link_to "Get a Valuation", tools_valuation_path,
        class: "rounded-sm bg-brand-300 px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-brand-900 hover:bg-white" %>
      <%= link_to "Speak With an Advisor", contact_path,
        class: "rounded-sm border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/10" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
